title: MAR 04 2022 - U.S. SHARES INTEL WITH UKRAINE
description:
White House Press Secretary Jen Psaki admits that the United States is sharing real-time intelligence with Ukraine, just as we learn that Russian and Ukrainian delegates agree to “humanitarian corridors”. All of this as U.S. virologist Jim LeDuc quietly calls for an investigation into multiple Chinese labs on the origins of the COVID-19 virus. Meanwhile, China plans to abolish restrictive family planning policies amid population crisis, and the Biden administration is attempting to make good on campaign promises by reviving and re-entering into the Iranian Nuclear Deal. 
Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
